>>+/*
>>+ * libqos driver framework
>>+ *
>>+ * Based on tests/qtest/libqos/virtio-blk.c
>>+ *
>>+ * Copyright (c) 2020 Coiby Xu <coiby.xu@gmail.com>
>>+ *
>>+ * Copyright (c) 2018 Emanuele Giuseppe Esposito <e.emanuelegiuseppe@gmail.com>
>>+ *
